The paper discusses a method for improving the quality of neural network predictors by incorporating target derivatives in addition to target values while training. This is relevant to several sub-fields of computer science, including machine learning (cs.LG), neural networks (cs.NE), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), computer vision (cs.CV), and control systems (cs.SY). Therefore, these are the most likely sub-categories for this paper.
